%C3%A1i-v%C3%A3ng-H%C3%A0-Th%C3%A0nh-k%C3%BD-ki%E1%BA%BFn/poem-C7j0EbeM3tsUWCFW_Tr3pg">Tái vãng Hà Thành ký kiến - 再往河城記見</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-B%E1%BA%A1ch-M%C3%A3-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C6%B0u/poem-dW9R6UpAsABiUgZsSbvYjA">Tặng Bạch Mã vương Bưu - 贈白馬王彪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%ABa-Th%E1%BA%A9m-b%C3%A1t-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BB%B9-tr%E1%BB%AB-thi%E1%BB%87n-b%E1%BB%99-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-tr%E1%BB%9F-v%C5%A9-v%E1%BB%8B-to%E1%BA%A1i-tr%C3%AC-h%E1%BA%A1-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-th%E1%BB%AD-thi/poem-rhRx6w9jswcvvfgNflryhQ">Thừa Thẩm bát trượng Đông Mỹ trừ thiện bộ viên ngoại, trở vũ vị toại trì hạ, phụng ký thử thi - 承沈八丈東美除膳部員外，阻雨未遂馳賀，奉寄此詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%BAng/T%E1%BB%89nh/poem-4vtEmU3ikDHwWFhwP-b7Ag">Tỉnh - 井</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%BAng/author-fNknbWPFKAJ0mVTedTVmZA">Nguyễn Thiên Túng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-huynh-d%E1%BB%AF-U%C3%BD-Chi-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-ki%E1%BA%BFn-chi%C3%AAu-ti%E1%BB%83u-%E1%BA%A9m-th%C3%AC-d%C6%B0-d%C4%A9-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-vong-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-W7SsPhc6WPfy8fWx-G66aw">Vương thập nhị huynh dữ Uý Chi viên ngoại tương phỏng, kiến chiêu tiểu ẩm, thì dư dĩ điệu vong nhật cận, bất khứ, nhân ký - 王十二兄與畏之員外相訪，見招小飲，時予以悼亡日近，不去，因寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBku